question: List all international baccalaureate programs and advanced placement programs with 30 credits.
sql_query1:
SELECT Education_Programs.name 
FROM Education_Programs
WHERE (Education_Programs.Type = "International Baccalaureate Program" OR Education_Programs.Type = "Advanced Placement Program") AND Education_Programs.Credits = 30
sql_query2:
SELECT Education_Programs.name 
FROM Education_Programs
WHERE Education_Programs.Type = "International Baccalaureate Program" OR Education_Programs.Type = "Advanced Placement Program" AND Education_Programs.Credits = 30
interpretation1: Which international baccalaureate programs have 30 credits and which advanced placement programs have the same number of credits?
interpretation2: Provide a list of international baccalaureate programs and also provide a list of advanced placement programs with 30 credits.
